rules:
## Zscaler: domains + IPs (one classical ruleset)
- RULE-SET,Zscaler,手动选择,no-resolve
## LinkedIn: stay on .com (DNS/hosts still in overwrite.sh)
- DOMAIN-SUFFIX,linkedin.com,全球代理
- DOMAIN-SUFFIX,licdn.com,全球代理
- DOMAIN-SUFFIX,linkedin.cn,REJECT
- DOMAIN-SUFFIX,licdn.cn,REJECT
## Apple TV+ / Music / News only; rest of Apple stays DIRECT
- RULE-SET,AppleMedia,手动选择
## Firstrade: CF App hosts → proxy; rest DIRECT (home IP)
- DOMAIN,api3x.firstrade.com,手动选择
- DOMAIN,streamingx.firstrade.com,手动选择
- DOMAIN,invest.firstrade.com,手动选择
- DOMAIN-SUFFIX,firstrade.com,DIRECT
- DOMAIN-SUFFIX,firstrade.net,DIRECT
## Mail SMTP → DIRECT (rule_provider/MailSMTP.yaml)
- RULE-SET,MailSMTP,DIRECT
## Rebrickable → url-test group (rule_provider/Rebrickable.yaml)
- RULE-SET,Rebrickable,Rebrickable
